<sec>
<st>
 Moqueca Baiana </st>
<p>

Influenced by <ethnic_group wordnetid="107967382" confidence="0.8">
<group wordnetid="100031264" confidence="0.8">
<people wordnetid="107942152" confidence="0.8">
<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../071/795071.xml">
African</link></people>
</group>
</ethnic_group>
 cuisine. In addition to the basic ingredients, <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../561/57561.xml">
palm oil</link> (<it>dendê</it>), <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../327/743327.xml">
coconut milk</link>, <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../138/52138.xml">
shrimp</link>, or <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../084/93084.xml">
crab</link> are added.</p>

